@startuml avataGeneration
title Sequence Diagram: Body Measurement Estimation and Avatar Generation

actor Customer

boundary "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend
control "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
control "Computer Vision\n(OpenCV + MediaPipe)" as CV
control "Avatar Generator\n(Three.js)" as Avatar
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Customer -> Frontend : Upload body video
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : Send video
activate Backend

Backend -> CV : Process uploaded video
activate CV

CV -> CV : Extract video frames
CV -> CV : Detect body landmarks
CV -> CV : Estimate body measurements

CV --> Backend : Return measurements
deactivate CV

Backend -> Avatar : Generate avatar
activate Avatar

Avatar --> Backend : Generated avatar
deactivate Avatar

Backend -> DB : Save avatar & measurements
activate DB

DB --> Backend : Saved successfully
deactivate DB

Backend --> Frontend : Return avatar
deactivate Backend

Frontend --> Customer : Display avatar
deactivate Frontend

@enduml